description:
ImgClip is a very simple picture cropping & picture compression tool.

【Features】

- Batch crop and compress pictures;
- Custom crop area, movable and stretchable crop area;
- Manual cropping mode, support manual cropping of a single picture;
- Provide multiple cutting styles for more convenient operation;
- The cropped and compressed pictures are still high-definition;
- After the operation is completed, the original image can be deleted;
- Support iPhone, iPad;
- Minimalist style, no in-app purchases, no ads;

If you like, you can introduce ImgClip to your friends as support.
